article1.author: Evan Haynos

headline.text: Meet two local artists who will showcase their art at Refinery29’s D.C. festival

article2.author: Joy Saha
article2.blurb: I recently had the pleasure to talk to Tenbeete Solomon — also known as Trap Bob — and Jamea Richmond-Edwards, two local artists who will be showcasing their artwork at the D.C. installation. The festival is held from Oct. 18 to Oct. 27.
